Invocation Name: flamingo facts
des:
Ask for flamingo Facts.

Flamingo Facts provides fun the whole family can enjoy and is guaranteed to make you smarter.

To start, just say "Alexa, launch Flamingo Facts" or "Alexa, open Flamingo Facts" to get a fact".

At anytime, you can stop by saying "Alexa, stop"
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
